-- hello.fl — A simple introduction to Fluent

Let name be "World".
Let greeting be "Hello".

Output "=== FLUENT Hello World ===".
Output greeting.
Output name.

-- Basic arithmetic
Let x be 10.
Let y be 32.
Let sum be x plus y.
Output sum.

-- A simple function
To greet a person (person_name):
    Output "Hello from Fluent,".
    Output person_name.
End of greet a person.

Let result be the result of greet a person "Harshal".
